#How to Use:

1.Either u run this python code in your system , it will work
make sure to #pip install psutil

2. another way is to make a binary executable(.exe) file and run as a indepedent file:
It is recommended way as it does not require any python or any other thing need to be installed
it only require that .exe file

now how to use:
download this info.exe and double click or
if you want to maek your own then,
->write this command:
pip install pyinstaller
pyinstaller --onefile system_scan.py

in your terminal
it will automatically create a .exe in dist folder in same directory.
